title: Longfellow House Washington's Headquarters National Historic Site: Photo Gallery
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia     Photo Gallery              Photo Gallery                    Japanese and Chinese Photographs   24 Photos  Selections from the 19th century Japanese and Chinese photograph collections at Longfellow National Historic Site.          Daguerreotypes and Ambrotypes   14 Photos  A selection of nineteenth century daguerreotypes and ambrotypes from the Longfellow National Historic Site's collection.          Longfellow Garden Flowers   91 Photos  The formal garden at Longfellow House-Washington's Headquarters is an ever-changing pageant of color.  Browse photos of some of the many flowers that bloom throughout the year.            NPS Centennial Media-Quality Photo Gallery   5 Photos  A selection of media quality site photographs.
